Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.30,0:00:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾有互相憎恨之人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.09,0:00:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尸腐于野 血染英魂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.30,0:00:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羁绊断于利刃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.70,0:00:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真心在黑暗中哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.41,0:00:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心爱之人 且赴黄泉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.34,0:02:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨恨我可就找错门了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.22,0:02:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要恨的话就恨德川吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.26,0:03:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恨骏府的家康大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.74,0:03:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恨将军继承人之争吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.32,0:03:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及 诅咒自己为何生在甲贺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.43,0:03:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.23,0:03:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漫长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.66,0:03:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一天 终于到来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.57,0:03:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豹马
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.82,0:04:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.93,0:04:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人——
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.91,0:04:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.00,0:05:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦…之…介
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.48,0:05:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧…小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.34,0:05:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.64,0:05:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.97,0:05:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你带着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.81,0:05:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.85,0:05:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧不见了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.78,0:06:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们说听见打斗的声音了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.44,0:06:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.57,0:06:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在那儿抖什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.30,0:06:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是胧出了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.62,0:06:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们怎么交待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.96,0:06:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我没有剑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.98,0:06:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请拿起剑吧 胧小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.55,0:06:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必须杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.92,0:06:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不得不置我于死地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.28,0:06:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许你能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.49,0:06:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今我的双目被封
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.98,0:06:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的双眼也看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.77,0:06:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊贺人干的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是我自己封住的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.03,0:07:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想目睹与卍谷人的争斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.88,0:07:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.90,0:07:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.34,0:07:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.34,0:07:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.96,0:07:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这双眼睛重见光明之前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.04,0:07:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.79,0:07:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.88,0:07:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲贺只剩我一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.31,0:07:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊贺也只剩下我一人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.63,0:08:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快拔剑啊 胧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.68,0:08:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.86,0:08:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳炎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.73,0:08:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不杀胧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.30,0:08:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您要背叛甲贺 背叛卍谷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.35,0:08:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.46,0:08:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背叛我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.42,0:08:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳炎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.85,0:08:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女人欺骗您 陷害您
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.28,0:08:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是锷隐的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.02,0:08:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.76,0:09:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就快动手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.54,0:09:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之…介
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.21,0:09:25.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.21,0:09:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我的…安居之所
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.25,0:09:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不存在于…此世
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.46,0:10:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.54,0:10:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.96,0:10:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.02,0:10:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就一个人活下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.00,0:10:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.10,0:10:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要——
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.68,0:10:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.19,0:11:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毒性…消失…了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.38,0:11:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.86,0:12:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.68,0:12:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.51,0:12:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.25,0:12:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.19,0:12:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想…我不想杀任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.06,0:12:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想让任何人死去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.36,0:12:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.79,0:13:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.73,0:13:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是甲贺人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.22,0:13:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲贺弦之介来过了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.23,0:13:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天膳大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.77,0:13:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天…天膳大人又死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.92,0:13:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫要惊慌失措
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.02,0:13:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天膳是不死的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.80,0:13:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不是都知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来人 扶他起来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.02,0:13:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那颗脑袋给他放回原处
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.38,0:13:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.19,0:14:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是关系到竹千代少爷 也关系到我阿福
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.27,0:14:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时也关系到你们命运的大事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.29,0:14:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.03,0:14:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.18,0:14:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 胧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.71,0:14:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要小心药师寺天膳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.51,0:15:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也许还没有见过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.06,0:15:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他会不死的秘术
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.33,0:15:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也非忍术范畴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.27,0:15:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的身体里寄宿着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.16,0:15:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道那究竟是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.16,0:15:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟那传说早在我出生之前就有了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.69,0:15:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有确认之术
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.03,0:15:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 依我之见 寄生在他体内的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.03,0:15:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.11,0:15:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不 说太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.27,0:15:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对今后路还长的你而言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.01,0:15:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有知道的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.53,0:16:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 我也老糊涂了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.80,0:16:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.10,0:16:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.96,0:16:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.86,0:16:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.77,0:16:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的眼睛能看见了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.45,0:17:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不太对劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.88,0:17:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天膳大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.19,0:17:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.98,0:17:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就藏在…胧身后…的台阶下…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.71,0:18:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对今后路还长的你而言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.47,0:18:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有知道的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.99,0:18:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾等甲贺卍谷一族
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.03,0:18:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊贺锷隐一族
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.85,0:19:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身怀可怕忍法秘术的双方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.21,0:19:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以长年宿怨为由
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.23,0:19:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互相憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.05,0:19:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实为愚蠢至极
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.09,0:19:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我如此认为
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.80,0:19:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对今后路还长的你而言
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.27,0:19:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我如此认为
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.80,0:19:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有知道的必要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.85,0:19:57.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想杀任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.22,0:20:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.70,0:20:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.15,0:20:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.25,0:20:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死…死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.83,0:20:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胧…胧呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.07,0:20:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方才天膳所说的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.25,0:20:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实 我的身后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.33,0:20:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躺着身受重伤又了中毒的甲贺人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.22,0:20:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 干得好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.09,0:21:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀死无反抗之力的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.57,0:21:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有损伊贺之名
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.40,0:21:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说…说什么话 一点不像忍者的作风
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.54,0:21:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.02,0:21:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火速派人报告服部半藏大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.76,0:21:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.46,0:21:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快备马
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.63,0:21:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在双方忍众仲裁的半藏大人面前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.29,0:21:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂堂正正地一决胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.13,0:21:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可有异议？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.80,0:21:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有…异议
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.25,0:23:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寂静暮春
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.35,0:23:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依然楚楚稚嫩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.24,0:23:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无垢的两个灵魂坠入蓝色冥暗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.22,0:23:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同转瞬即逝的泡影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.38,0:23:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消逝在青蓝月辉的他界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.58,0:23:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深藏于心的羁绊 飘摇的悲恋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.01,0:23:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数度轮回之后再续前缘
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.91,0:23:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跨越千万暗夜再结连理
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.15,0:24:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,basilisk 甲贺忍法帖
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.25,0:24:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终话
